Introduced in the [https://docs.vrchat.com/docs/vrchat-202123 Identity Update], user profiles are a personalized space where information is displayed about a user. Information on a user's profile includes [[Special:MyLanguage/Social#Statuses|status]], [[Special:MyLanguage/Trust_Rank|trust rank]], [[Special:MyLanguage/Social#Pronouns|pronouns]], bio, current [[Special:MyLanguage/Instances|instance]] (if applicable), languages they speak, social links, [[Special:MyLanguage/Badges|badges]] they own, and the [[Special:MyLanguage/Groups|groups]] they're in.